snippet.textDisplay:
No doubt Kailash ji is an exceptional singer but can we please take a moment to bow to his composition, which he has composed himself beautifully unlike today's composers who just know how to ruin a masterpiece by adding mechanical things and no real instruments and OFCOURSE his LYRIC WRITING, I mean he is the singer, composer as well as the lyricist, that makes this song more beautiful and special.
He truly signifies how a musician should be like, not like Tonny Kakkar who also sings,writes and composes but his songs are worse then shitt...
What can I say for Kailash ji he is a underrated living legend and I never wanted to compare him to Tonny or any other pseudo-musician of today's time but had to give this for reference. I think I should stop now else I can keep writing or end up writing a book on the appreciation of this song and obviously Kailash ji,too good in the last😌😌😌❤️
